vulkan-smoketest is a specialized utility used to verify the proper
installation and functionality of the Vulkan graphics API. It provides
a short rendering test to ensure that the drivers, GPU, and system
libraries are communicating correctly.

Additional Notes:
* This package requires a GPU with Vulkan support and the appropriate
  kernel drivers (such as amdgpu, nvidia, or i915) to be loaded before
  execution.
* Ensure your user is a member of the 'video' group to allow direct
  access to the rendering hardware.
